# Fractional-Knapsack-Implementation
An implementation of fractional knapsack problem.

## Example problem

| Object | 1  | 2 | 3 |
|--------|----|---|---|
| Profit | 15 | 6 | 9 |
| Weight | 3  | 2 | 1 |
